Hello,Social,is,a,social,promotion,and,engagement,platform,that,lets,brands,and,companies,engage,and,interact,with,their,customers,and,potential,customers,with,social,promotions,and,contests,The,Hello,Social,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Hello,Social,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,managing,promotions,creating,promotions,and,managing,account,information